[[File:ASAOutside.JPG|thumb|right|View of the crowd outside [[ASA Hall of Fame Stadium]] on August 22, 2007]] The third '''[[World Cup of Softball]]''' was held in [[Oklahoma City, Oklahoma]] USA between July 12 and July 16, 2007. USA won their second World Cup by defeating Japan 3-0 in the Championship Game.
